    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what u mean about it being a double edged sword, but it feels like the \"higher prices\" argument is always used to shut down any talk of protecting workers. isn't it basically true that if we don't use tariffs, we're just letting overseas companies destroy our own manufacturing base?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
