      "role": "user",
      "content": "that seems like a very pro-tariff way of looking at it. most economists say that's not how it works and that the trade-offs are way worse for the average person. don't you think the 'innovate or die' logic is just a way to ignore the actual suffering and job loss that happens when we close off trade?",
